"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[change] Architecture documentation updated: The technical architecture and design principles for Hive-Mind v2.0.0 were read and documented. This includes an overview of its purpose as a universal, distributed, and multimodal memory layer for AI agents, addressing continuity and collective intelligence. The core components, such as the Unified Memory Core (UMC) based on SQLite, Model Sovereignty (Hive-Dreamer), P2P Swarm Synchronization, and Multimodality, are explained. The document also details the memory write and read paths, failure handling strategies, and key Architectural Decision Records (ADRs) that shaped the system's design. Finally, the directory structure is presented for clarity.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1ltedzf","at":1782088670972},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.03976098,0.02850923,0.04384658,-0.053428,-0.03660691,0.08975853,-0.05322526,-0.01276971,0.03779126,-0.0081644,0.04996792,-0.05299475,0.02028472,0.01542599,0.01062418,0.01947596,-0.01482833,0.01296019,0.07050886,0.0260214,0.03095479,-0.05214827,-0.00149488,0.00322046,-0.01692176,0.07586644,-0.03343249,-0.01358746,-0.06853481,-0.24478926,0.05792212,-0.01537006,0.03676155,0.01050013,-0.02931303,-0.02801064,0.01878894,0.01525445,-0.03867749,0.02606943,-0.02663283,0.02101054,-0.00129593,0.00401493,-0.04036593,-0.00023327,-0.01874167,-0.0558065,-0.06448346,-0.09012281,-0.05469726,0.0337044,-0.01267164,0.00778306,-0.00152054,0.08907457,-0.00545741,0.04701778,0.04023353,0.03223832,0.06046648,0.03403197,-0.18373221,0.10010493,0.11676739,0.03362565,-0.05196911,-0.03354504,0.02126496,0.01444892,-0.04739366,0.00230775,0.05565621,0.03200608,0.03969293,0.00806416,-0.05127971,-0.03939105,0.01126841,-0.04895502,-0.01993022,-0.00928197,-0.02911422,-0.03907906,-0.02121794,-0.00091302,-0.00140851,-0.00698913,-0.00413958,0.00437427,-0.00190499,0.05760796,0.00081419,0.01631136,-0.03909771,