"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[bugfix] LanceDB Store Initialization Failure: The system encountered a critical IO error within the LanceDB store during the initial indexing/scanning phase. This \"Invalid range\" memory error typically occurs when the indexer attempts to process files that are either empty, corrupted, or excessively large, leading to a crash in the Rust-based Lance library. To resolve this and enable successful embedding generation, the project requires a configuration of .kilocodeignore to exclude heavy files and directories that are not necessary for the LLM's context but are triggering the LanceDB failure.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"eqizqx","at":1782088671118},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.08040466,-0.03658586,0.03083808,-0.06849451,0.01581119,-0.04162427,-0.08244825,-0.02448749,0.00819682,0.01077367,0.05664502,-0.04030436,0.08774194,0.02764966,-0.02186652,0.00932361,-0.00812053,-0.0053596,0.06477617,0.04382208,0.0675801,-0.022168,-0.00270379,-0.01210175,-0.04550381,0.13923664,-0.03099362,-0.05758197,-0.09394146,-0.27106881,-0.00574363,-0.03782736,0.08451802,0.00454664,-0.00655965,-0.04133883,-0.02239879,0.0143943,-0.01705671,0.02907019,-0.01061504,0.01270942,-0.06633004,-0.00135209,-0.03743416,-0.073622,0.00395035,-0.01206974,0.06047351,-0.04306795,-0.10158106,0.00830526,0.00470619,-0.0246182,0.0239176,0.04835024,0.0599668,0.07773306,0.05273771,0.02297692,0.06232968,-0.0230005,-0.15949383,0.07312076,0.02383458,0.04563826,-0.02457349,-0.03010901,0.04469322,-0.02065223,-0.06697002,-0.04570908,0.01728439,0.09200539,-0.01261234,-0.00162646,0.01390574,0.02850347,0.01840412,0.01565029,0.02304348,-0.03040392,0.02310545,-0.02585811,-0.02190854,-0.03548855,-0.01132575,0.02789544,0.04771774,-0.00867085,0.02781932,-0.01308846,0.0147273,0.00690115,-0.03813936,-0.0160691,0.03270079,0.02513144,-0.07929435,0.13359402,-0.00832627,-0.00185878,0.01036733,-0.0026703,0.0