"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[discovery] Analysis of run_comfyui.sh Path Handling: The analysis of `run_comfyui.sh` reveals that the script is designed for portability, dynamically calculating the project directory and updating the virtual environment's configuration to match the current location. Crucially, there is no evidence of hardcoded paths referencing `/run/media/` within this script. This suggests that the discrepancy between `/media/` and `/run/media/` is likely introduced either by the OS mount point behavior, a configuration file read by `main.py`, or the `run_comfyui_smart.sh` variant.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"r03mpo","at":1782088671209},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07412522,-0.01967476,0.05127855,-0.03726601,0.02194583,0.04606803,-0.07941325,-0.03440102,-0.0341772,-0.02047726,0.04377936,-0.01822319,0.06099131,-0.00954043,-0.02735283,0.00441163,-0.00160501,0.06801691,0.09848844,0.06163147,0.07087149,-0.00800517,0.0684096,-0.04147144,-0.01731901,0.08549558,0.03884352,-0.0410021,-0.0575484,-0.2153839,-0.00506277,-0.02971579,0.03812901,-0.00949148,0.02689923,-0.0225793,-0.01015906,0.04625689,0.0021519,0.07051476,0.04102797,0.02021587,0.02118096,0.01330984,-0.01093304,-0.04989595,-0.03372048,-0.04917246,-0.00812891,-0.07928237,-0.07939524,-0.01113477,-0.01324206,-0.02022795,-0.02307075,0.04644831,0.07264517,0.03551623,0.01701277,0.05081644,0.00294886,0.089366,-0.2053939,0.0622991,0.11508162,-0.01035065,-0.02671064,-0.02546624,-0.01897322,0.0292256,-0.14201723,0.00988454,0.00768522,0.03426557,0.01569613,-0.06713978,-0.031603,0.00874907,-0.05206226,-0.03611601,0.03149755,-0.00981431,-0.03920509,0.06286935,-0.02007703,-0.03308517,-0.00529453,0.02955673,0.0518724,0.09778581,0.02171242,-0.05148849,0.00982828,0.05450356,-0.03358706,-0.01749945,-0.00157492,0.02327438,-0.02977574,0.1070217,-0.06986403,-0.02424209,0.00499733,-0.00369126,0.063259,-0.00139841,0.0215599