"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[security_alert] Google client_secret hardcoded and compromised: The Google OAuth client_secret was found to be hardcoded directly within the application's source code. This is a critical security vulnerability, as it exposes the secret to anyone who can access the code. A manual intervention was necessary to revoke the compromised client_secret and generate a new one. The new secret must be securely stored in the environment variable GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET in the .env file to prevent future exposure.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"81jkqt","at":1782088671253},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.01993173,-0.06787848,-0.02081247,-0.08791131,0.01431935,0.03697458,0.0423282,0.00002561,-0.04358659,0.02853997,-0.03908009,-0.03185768,0.0152187,0.04338362,0.00627918,-0.00688738,0.02658018,0.0203041,0.00741269,0.05656857,0.09649473,-0.0033098,0.04488841,0.01520702,-0.01208899,0.07552141,-0.04405269,-0.06382097,-0.04859898,-0.13560207,0.01528273,-0.03128909,0.01461248,0.01562965,0.02389473,-0.04392685,-0.05221477,0.04338736,-0.03075116,0.0650923,0.03014647,-0.00873336,-0.03110723,-0.04959911,-0.00330499,-0.02014523,-0.05696993,0.00668529,-0.00015795,-0.05385508,0.01537466,0.06627061,0.0126382,0.05874309,0.00067824,-0.05349671,0.03350681,0.0772528,-0.01150232,0.13247852,0.0184103,0.05361,-0.16032504,0.05456351,0.07231064,0.13325031,-0.07388379,-0.02647419,0.0409858,0.01081119,-0.07900119,-0.00810363,-0.04714993,0.02422086,0.02795485,-0.03559355,-0.01232161,0.00162577,-0.01530373,-0.04853925,-0.0047888,0.00396382,0.01753785,-0.00578737,-0.03541776,-0.06643256,0.01003547,0.01651095,0.07200573,0.00745217,-0.01560942,-0.06737969,0.00135657,0.0172907,-0.02121065,-0.00162531,-0.02968823,0.0506791,-0.10131236,0.14169525,-0.04936145,0.01767443,-0.03066827,-0.06279057,0.06365979,-0.06463806,0.05723966,-0.04345697,-0.04253534,0.04029132,0.01368783,0.00357023,0.0322090