"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[discovery] OpenAlice UI Component Architecture and Design Tokens: An exploration of the OpenAlice UI source code revealed a modular component architecture. The system utilizes a mix of shared utility components (like the Market Card) and specialized feature-based components. Data visualization is handled by Recharts, with a consistent theme applied through CSS variables for colors and borders. The workspace and market modules contain the bulk of the complex UI logic, including panels for financial statements, key metrics, and klines.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1o3ax8r","at":1782088671347},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05668608,-0.0199329,0.02694941,-0.03080371,-0.01017537,-0.00500568,-0.02106098,0.02092291,0.01660777,0.00615268,-0.01578504,-0.05219906,0.03187773,0.06273104,0.02809089,-0.00608124,-0.02633925,0.02099706,0.01962505,0.01229568,0.07421727,-0.08546143,0.01948172,-0.03879228,-0.00857028,0.11799631,-0.0589001,-0.09351244,0.01634668,-0.22773246,0.01425134,0.01453495,0.09850218,-0.02165342,-0.06546539,-0.02489702,-0.02824817,0.02400042,-0.02022299,0.03621748,-0.03259064,0.00754295,-0.01108474,-0.03657959,-0.01663261,-0.02147572,-0.0365558,-0.00768294,-0.03867107,-0.00044776,-0.02946696,-0.01792716,-0.02652366,0.04978885,0.0528508,0.10253634,0.01504291,0.01440576,-0.00403217,0.08238083,0.02263873,0.02352069,-0.16738349,0.15619393,0.044092,0.03355263,-0.00136601,0.01853468,0.04344924,-0.0137427,-0.02616296,0.02197886,0.04321781,-0.00123877,-0.01667621,-0.03350941,0.03710961,-0.03470544,-0.0085814,-0.02399289,-0.00507183,-0.00250362,0.01464398,0.00237912,0.00113891,-0.0135649,-0.02139634,0.02157312,0.04391456,-0.00623744,-0.02982494,-0.03785298,0.02315299,-0.02182692,-0.07842829,0.01259224,-0.0221085,0.02274686,-0.02848142,0.1543472,-0.07143912,0.00556895,0.05258044,-0.02991282,0.06246969,-0.02330926,0.04044181,0.01257735,-0.05637246,0.