"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[decision] TTS Integration Architecture and Strategy: The TTS integration strategy moves Thoth from a standalone prototype (`tts_bridge.go`) to a fully integrated runtime system. By treating Kokoro and Qwen3 as native providers, the system maintains a consistent interface while leveraging specialized Python SDKs. The use of build tags allows the binary to remain lean for users who do not require audio capabilities. The integration involves updating the gateway contract to handle audio attachments and implementing specific channel adapters (Telegram, WhatsApp) to support voice delivery.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"11fo7z","at":1782088671381},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.0693807,0.00529141,0.02948328,-0.01660569,-0.04855664,-0.01848138,-0.046957,0.01985622,0.03905611,0.04972541,0.05073796,-0.03553784,0.02963522,0.03487243,0.05093294,-0.00706727,-0.0064619,0.0051653,0.07355879,0.01374699,0.0209787,-0.01191007,0.02633979,0.02490956,-0.01591492,0.08184127,-0.02288016,-0.03939547,-0.02027389,-0.1950774,0.06591001,-0.04182448,-0.00618695,-0.04562674,-0.02277594,0.01359893,-0.07277916,-0.00919176,-0.02183712,0.0560599,-0.01237682,0.04189054,0.00618502,-0.09105089,-0.056247,-0.03703367,-0.05189313,-0.03011925,-0.0269365,-0.02521332,-0.0427075,-0.01277103,0.00898756,0.00153572,-0.03708248,0.08857118,0.06722328,0.09118234,0.030587,0.06491809,0.05614853,-0.01694493,-0.18165432,0.12638257,0.01795519,0.08856212,-0.02104128,0.06076837,0.03142526,0.06174159,-0.0715441,0.01613266,0.03193295,0.02001123,0.02994619,-0.01186728,0.04884093,-0.00907947,0.01581989,-0.01595374,0.01674243,-0.01548194,-0.01158387,-0.01952288,-0.03264315,-0.02686642,-0.05014651,-0.03551602,-0.03140401,0.03471974,-0.03849773,-0.00296191,0.02700625,-0.01108589,-0.00714554,-0.01844814,0.03421762,-0.02363462,-0.03654193,0.08888612,0.00785005,0.01088278,0.00035542,-0.01487964,0.04504374,-0.