"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[discovery] Analysis of run_comfyui_smart.sh: The analysis of `run_comfyui_smart.sh` confirms that it is a high-level wrapper for VRAM and performance optimization. It does not manipulate paths beyond determining its own location to call the primary `run_comfyui.sh` script. Since neither the smart launcher nor the primary startup script contain the problematic `/run/media/` path, the issue must reside within the Python application logic (specifically how it resolves user paths) or the environment in which the process is executed.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"ja8aym","at":1782088671666},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05445444,0.04761663,0.06977994,-0.02697156,-0.0155805,0.04122024,-0.06119448,0.01546833,-0.02463797,-0.00043887,0.02886543,-0.02084888,0.04795089,0.02203821,0.00371246,0.00099066,-0.00011381,0.04421741,0.10125543,0.06235883,0.05891826,-0.03389738,0.02792159,-0.06565937,-0.03959895,0.04412899,0.02050903,-0.06011662,-0.05127059,-0.22609197,0.01955761,-0.07769128,0.0450323,-0.01164872,0.01782516,-0.00046663,-0.00024532,0.06509031,0.01215648,0.05088393,0.03116248,0.02744059,0.00421769,0.03087244,0.01038709,-0.03973534,-0.02673985,-0.05526059,-0.04207981,-0.06190219,-0.04662155,-0.00130855,-0.02248519,-0.01262058,-0.02062314,0.02426037,0.06108707,0.02995479,-0.00165863,0.04209185,-0.02235146,0.07322112,-0.21405448,0.08942476,0.08635236,-0.01450083,-0.02351566,-0.06150569,-0.00341775,0.02794779,-0.10389042,0.02074091,0.04918771,0.02886728,0.01711585,-0.05319999,-0.04501249,0.00520919,-0.0265265,-0.00510658,0.02371076,-0.01704535,-0.05438988,0.07478502,0.01162134,-0.00043185,0.00908403,0.0182232,0.06226218,0.07976931,0.0390748,-0.00856644,0.01026083,0.03267952,-0.03161854,0.00855557,0.01498662,-0.00880879,-0.0640242,0.11420309,-0.04194585,-0.01718486,-0.01311892,0.00413782,0.04810013,0.00892234,0.02238341,-0.03856229,0.03843089,0.00232522,