"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[security_alert] Google client_secret hardcoded and compromised: The Google OAuth client_secret was discovered to be hardcoded directly within the application's source code. This poses a significant security risk, as it means the secret is exposed and should be considered compromised. A manual intervention is required to revoke the existing client_secret within the Google Cloud Console and generate a new one. This new secret must then be securely stored in the project's environment variables, specifically by updating the `GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET` variable in the `.env` file.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"13bm1r8","at":1782088671702},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.00518408,-0.0799048,-0.01305041,-0.08208054,0.02327526,0.02683172,0.05529192,0.00092573,-0.04142646,0.02800289,-0.03659603,-0.02627985,0.01026639,0.04249312,0.00498194,0.00098924,0.02002693,0.01444715,-0.00386375,0.04602863,0.08971113,0.004791,0.04897146,0.0116952,-0.00800353,0.07904129,-0.04995682,-0.06718461,-0.04658407,-0.13941735,0.01328077,-0.03075447,-0.00070681,0.0128209,0.02160449,-0.0445566,-0.04256257,0.03564648,-0.03675937,0.05756116,0.02710817,-0.01580937,-0.03431033,-0.05672014,-0.00236684,-0.03690295,-0.06264487,0.0042756,-0.02964156,-0.03460676,0.02289032,0.04583704,0.00862664,0.05565726,0.00650284,-0.0438261,0.04662165,0.08917553,-0.01324217,0.14727199,0.01631431,0.05354015,-0.16627781,0.05061812,0.08333319,0.12514123,-0.08582724,-0.03467202,0.04681788,0.01432281,-0.08534536,0.00786994,-0.05850548,0.03213265,0.03073903,-0.03056987,-0.01385721,-0.00399385,-0.01280533,-0.04364423,0.02143857,0.012318,0.02154436,0.00811321,-0.04799405,-0.08192942,0.01544103,0.01177501,0.05996175,0.01064317,-0.0165921,-0.06953472,-0.00506149,0.03160638,-0.01630506,0.01041614,-0.02768798,0.04867824,-0.10564233,0.13756938,-0.06278437,0.00822011,-0.0346056,-0.05330914,0.06755711,-0.06860573,0