"smart_blocks:cortex/parietal/inbox/2026/06/21/0300-session.md#Sessão Episódica: 2026-06-21 03:00#[bugfix] Fix password hashing inconsistency: A bug related to password handling has been fixed. Previously, different hashing algorithms or implementations might have been used for hashing passwords during registration and verifying them during login, leading to authentication failures. The system has been standardized to use bcrypt consistently for both operations, ensuring secure and reliable password management.": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1ddkhfk","at":1782088671740},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06765581,-0.01749029,-0.00541764,-0.08186308,-0.08252457,-0.01102971,0.03765655,-0.04938595,-0.00156715,0.02371895,0.01567097,-0.05447381,0.05206936,0.03186407,-0.00257031,0.01876079,-0.01878138,0.01738954,0.04397734,0.04925641,0.03695041,0.00063854,0.04885065,-0.0046386,-0.04870617,0.06684242,-0.02573579,-0.07054808,-0.03556647,-0.2286447,0.01809056,-0.00709583,0.01257943,-0.0344991,-0.01557542,0.0064239,-0.03772531,0.04674352,-0.01488056,0.05170175,-0.00837873,0.03613494,0.0053027,-0.0292612,-0.00843144,-0.01795429,-0.03129882,-0.03747762,0.04329348,-0.03150479,-0.03972422,0.02927952,0.06251576,0.03405175,0.02314645,0.03810732,0.01952766,0.07185325,0.01978034,0.06314235,0.05102534,0.04803903,-0.17696102,0.11299009,0.10750754,0.04560937,0.01443562,-0.0732526,0.02293813,0.07389884,-0.03650603,-0.01746655,-0.00628867,0.10349077,0.01772719,-0.00076367,-0.0226847,-0.05558189,-0.02487943,-0.06361334,-0.01941055,0.00758263,0.04980496,-0.00840697,-0.00192557,-0.0509718,-0.00745237,-0.01286261,0.01983788,-0.02440404,0.02515647,0.03711888,0.00096126,0.04557957,-0.07106789,-0.03910455,0.02739939,0.02397424,-0.12505014,0.12245306,-0.02487677,0.01659573,-0.02371311,-0.06959384,0.07097082,-0.01039568,0.01420359,-0.06643161,-0.07037813,-0.02153612,0.03080639,-0.01171428,0.09697232,-0.01839133,0.01416402,0.00591755,0.01009532,0.02939916,-0.00796916,0.0356756,0